### Spring Boot Application - API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Hello Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hello

### Generate Embedding - Simple Example
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/embedding
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sentence": "Hello, how are you?"
}

### Generate Embedding - Longer Text
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/embedding
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sentence": "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog."
}

### Generate Embedding - Technical Text
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/embedding
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sentence": "Machine learning models require large amounts of training data to achieve good performance."
}

### Generate Embedding - Question
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/embedding
