### Match Words - Simple
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/embedding/match-words
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sentence": "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog",
  "targets": ["animal", "speed", "color", "sleepy"],
  "threshold": 0.3,
  "topK": 2
}

### Match Words - Technical
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/embedding/match-words
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sentence": "Neural networks learn hierarchical representations from data.",
  "targets": ["biology", "learning", "representation", "data"],
  "threshold": 0.55,
  "topK": 3
}

### Cache Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/embedding/cache-stats

### Access Frequencies
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/embedding/access-frequencies

### Clear All Caches
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/embedding/clear-cache

### Clear Sentence Cache Only
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/embedding/clear-sentence-cache
